raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "cdshealpix" %}
{% set version = "0.8.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/cdshealpix-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 317b14ac49ad560e5f8f0cb01eee23910419130e1bd854d317d85d85d502c36a

build:
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - python                                 # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - cross-python_{{ target_platform }}     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - crossenv                               # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - maturin >=1.3.2,<2                     # [build_platform != target_platform]
    - {{ compiler("c") }}
    - {{ stdlib("c") }}
    - {{ compiler("rust") }}
  host:
    - pip
    - toml
    - maturin >=1.3.2,<2
    - python
  run:
    - astropy-base
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - cdshealpix
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip
    - python
    - pytest

about:
  home: https://pypi.org/project/cdshealpix/
  summary: Python cdshealpix package wrapping code of the cdshealpix crate.
